-- Bloomberg's Jaroslovsky Looks at Devices From 2010 CES: Video
-- 
-- 2010-01-15T05:18:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-01-15/bloomberg-s-jaroslovsky-looks-at-devices-from-2010-ces-video.html

          
          
             Bloomberg's Rich Jaroslovsky reviews
a selection of new devices he discovered last week at the 
Consumer Electronics Show in Las Vegas.  
 Jaroslovsky discusses an ultra-thin television manufactured
by LG Electronics Inc., an $11,000 personal sauna, tablet and 
netbook computers from Korea and a hat designed to optimize 
viewing video on the iPhone. (Source: Bloomberg)  
 
